  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.801,
    "endTime": 55.488,
    "text": "I'm on it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.423,
    "endTime": 63.963,
    "text": "So, to my fellow bean lovers, I say, \"Ich bean ein bean-liner.\""
